room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: It was our first time going here in Chicago and the experience was amazing! Had so much fun! I highly recommend trying this place out.

room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: A must experience in Chicago! The staff are friendly, helpful, and witty. Great time for everyone in our group and we'll definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "Jurassic Escape" by Escape the Room Chicago in Chicago
review: We had a team outing here and it was really really fun! They have a variety of rooms to choose from, the staff is really friendly, and the set up is unique from other escape rooms I've been too.I would definitely go back with another group!
